### Hadith 4:618

*Narrated Jabir bin 'Abdullah:*

We were with Allah's Apostle picking the fruits of the 'Arak trees, and
Allah's Apostle said, "Pick the black fruit, for it is the best." The
companions asked, "Were you a shepherd?" He replied, "There was no
prophet who was not a shepherd."

